          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "High-accuracy angular distribution measurements at 90",
                " degrees   were  performed  for  the  1-H-2(g,n)1-H-1",
                " reaction throughout the energy range  4-18  MeV  and",
                " for reaction angles of 45, 135, and 155 degrees.",
                "The results  indicate  a  significant  departure from",
                " existing theoretical  calculations  below  a  photon",
                " energy of 10 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
